==============Quotes===============
We need to eat and drink enough so that our strength is restored, and not suppressed.
To be content with what we possess is the greatest and most secure of riches.
Friendship improves happiness, and abates misery, by doubling our joys, and dividing our grief.
The face is a picture of the mind with the eyes as its interpreter.
Knowledge is a wealth that cannot be stolen.
There are two ways to be folled. One is to believe what isn't true, the other is to refuse to believe what is true.
It is better to try something and fail than to try nothing and succeed. The result may be the same, but you won't be. We always grow more through defeats than victories.
Face the facts of being what you are, for that is what changes what you are.
Take a chance and you may lose. Take not a chance and you have lost already.